OL,3,CEarly blood sugar control for type 2
OL,4,Cdiabetes 'can lead to fewer deaths'
OL,6,FTreating type 2 diabetes patients as
OL,7,Fearly as possible by controlling blood
OL,8,Fsugar with insulin and drugs can
OL,9,Fprevent heart attacks, kidney failure,
OL,10,Fvision loss and premature death,
OL,11,Faccording to long-running research.
OL,13,FScientists from the Universities of
OL,14,FOxford and Edinburgh analysed data
OL,15,Fspanning more than four decades from
OL,16,Fthe UK Prospective Diabetes Study
OL,17,F(UKPDS) ` one of the longest type 2
OL,18,Fdiabetes clinical trials.
