OL,3,CEarly blood sugar control for type 2
OL,4,Cdiabetes 'can lead to fewer deaths'
OL,6,FThe findings showed controlling blood
OL,7,Fglucose early, with either insulin
OL,8,Finjections or tablets that stimulate
OL,9,Fcells to make more insulin such as
OL,10,Fsulfonylureas, led to 10% fewer
OL,11,Fdeaths, 17% fewer heart attacks and
OL,12,F26% fewer diabetic complications.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, using metformin, a drug
OL,15,Fwhich helps the insulin the body
OL,16,Fproduces work better, led to 31% fewer
OL,17,Fheart attacks and 20% fewer deaths.
