OL,6,FProfessor Rury Holman, the founding
OL,7,Fdirector of the University of Oxford
OL,8,FDiabetes Trials Unit and chief
OL,9,Finvestigator of the UKPDS, said:
OL,10,F"These remarkable findings emphasise
OL,11,Fthe critical importance of detecting
OL,12,Fand treating type 2 diabetes
OL,13,Fintensively at the earliest possible
OL,14,Fopportunity.
OL,16,F"People may have type 2 diabetes for
OL,17,Fseveral years before being diagnosed
OL,18,Fas they may have few symptoms until
OL,19,Ftheir blood sugars become
OL,20,Fsubstantially elevated."
