OL,3,CEarly blood sugar control for type 2
OL,4,Cdiabetes 'can lead to fewer deaths'
OL,6,FThe UKPDS trial first began in 1977,
OL,7,Fwhere newly-diagnosed type 2 diabetes
OL,8,Fpatients were assigned to either
OL,9,Fintensive or conventional blood
OL,10,Fglucose control strategy.
OL,12,FThe intensive strategy involved using
OL,13,Fsulfonylurea or insulin therapy, or
OL,14,Fmetformin therapy, to control blood
OL,15,Fglucose while the standard method
OL,16,Finvolved making changes to diet.
