OL,3,CEarly blood sugar control for type 2
OL,4,Cdiabetes 'can lead to fewer deaths'
OL,6,FFindings showed that compared with
OL,7,Fdiet, controlling blood glucose with
OL,8,Fsulfonylurea or insulin, or with
OL,9,Fmetformin, showed a lifelong reduced
OL,10,Frisk of early death and heart attack.
OL,12,FGuidelines were later changed
OL,13,Fworldwide to recommend these intensive
OL,14,Ftherapies for everyone with type 2
OL,15,Fdiabetes.
