OL,6,FProfessor Amanda Adler, director of
OL,7,Fthe Diabetes Trial Unit, said: "This
OL,8,Fshows that treating type 2 diabetes
OL,9,Fearly and thoroughly is crucial.
OL,10,FPlaying catch-up with blood glucose
OL,11,Fcontrol is not sufficient."
OL,13,FProfessor Philip Clarke, director of
OL,14,Fthe University of Oxford Health
OL,15,FEconomics Research Centre, said: "A
OL,16,Fmajor life-time benefit is the
OL,17,Fincreased life-expectancy in those
OL,18,Fallocated to intensive blood glucose
OL,19,Fcontrol.
